!! SWM1: Configuracion de EtherChannel (LACP) hacia SWM2
config t

!! 1. Agrupar las interfaces fisicas
int range e0/1-3
description Enlaces fisicos LACP hacia SWM2
channel-protocol lacp
channel-group 1 mode active
exit

!! 2. Configurar la interfaz logica (Port-Channel)
int port-channel 1
description EtherChannel Troncal a SWM2
switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk native vlan 99
switchport trunk allowed vlan 10,20,60,70,80,90,99
exit
do wr